content.rendered:
Directed by Oliver Parker.

Written by Morwenna Banks. Morwenna Banks. Nick Hornby.

Cast Tom Bateman (Clive). David Threlfall (George Parker). Rosie Cavaliero (Aunty Marie). Morwenna Banks (Patsy). Rupert Everett (Brian Debenham). Leo Bill (Tony). Alexa Davies (Marjorie). Arsher Ali (Dennis). Matthew Beard (Bill). Clare-Hope Ashitey (Diane). Alistair Petrie (Ted Sargent). Emily Bevan (Edith). Rosa Coduri (Polly). Kyle Pryor (Aiden). Doon Mackichan (Miss Sykes). Lottie Tolhurst (Jill). Manpreet Bambra (Anya). Laura Joy Pieters (Millie). Ross Berkeley Simpson (Warm Up Man). Kenneth Collard (Bert Redwood). Emma Davies (Beryl). John Hopkins (Andrew O’Shea). Daniel Crossley (Len Phillips). Connor Hewitt (AFM). Karen Young (Sal). Kate Crossley (Pat- Woman worker 1). Alexis Tuttle (Eunice). Elliot James Langridge (Terry Clarke).

Language English.

Producers Gemma Arterton. Morwenna Banks. Andrea Calderwood. Gail Egan. Lois Frost. Joanna Hughes. Jessica Malik. Jessica Parker. Paul Schlesinger. Chloe Sizer. Ross Williams. Nick Hornby.

Production Potboiler Television. Rebel Park Productions. SKY Studios.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 6

Status OnGoing (2023–)
